# /onboarding
msgid "Welcome to <1>Big River Watch</1>!"
msgstr "Croeso i'r arolwg <1>Big River Watch</1>!"

# /onboarding
msgid ""
"Take part in the survey to help us understand the health of our rivers."
msgstr "Cymerwch ran yn yr arolwg i'n helpu i ddeall iechyd ein hafonydd."

# /onboarding
msgid ""
"Simply sign up and pick a riverside location that you can spend 10-15 mins "
"observing."
msgstr ""
"Cofrestrwch a dewiswch leoliad glan afon y gallwch dreulio 10-15 munud yn ei"
" arsylwi."

# /onboarding
msgid ""
"Look out for things like wildlife, plants and pollution, then start the "
"survey in this app to tell us what you can see. Click ‘submit’ to send us "
"your results!"
msgstr ""
"Cadwch olwg am bethau fel bywyd gwyllt, planhigion a llygredd. Cwblhewch yr "
"arolwg yn yr ap hwn i roi gwybod i ni'r hyn y gallwch ei weld. Cliciwch ar "
"'cyflwyno' i anfon eich canlyniadau atom!"

# /onboarding
msgid "Not sure what you’re looking at?"
msgstr "Ddim yn siŵr beth rydych chi'n edrych arno?"

# /onboarding
msgid ""
"Use our handy ID guides to help identify some of the different species or "
"types of pollution you might come across."
msgstr ""
"Defnyddiwch ein canllawiau defnyddiol i'ch helpu i adnabod rhai o'r gwahanol"
" rywogaethau neu wahanol fathau o lygredd y gallech ddod ar eu traws."

# /onboarding
msgid ""
"Remember, you should never enter the river to take part in <2>Big River "
"Watch</2>."
msgstr ""
"Cofiwch: ni ddylech fyth fynd i mewn i afon wrth gymryd rhan yn <2>Big River"
" Watch</2>."

# /onboarding
msgid ""
"Find somewhere safe nearby to the river where there is no risk of slipping "
"into the water, and enjoy a peaceful time observing river life."
msgstr ""
"Chwliwch am fan diogel wrth ymyl afon lle nad oes unrhyw berygl o lithro i'r"
" dŵr. Mwynhewch amser hamddenol yn arsylwi bywyd yr afon."

# /onboarding
msgid ""
"Click to confirm you’ve read the <2>Health and Safety guidance</2> and you "
"agree to our <6>Terms and Conditions</6>."
msgstr ""
"Cliciwch i gadarnhau eich bod wedi darllen y <2>canllawiau Iechyd a "
"Diogelwch</2> a'ch bod yn cytuno â'n<6>Telerau ac Amodau</6>."

